{"type":null,"faqId":49384,"title":"手势控制","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.20833333in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:13pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.4763889in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p6{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s3{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"手势控制\"XE \"动作控制\"XE \"翻转静音\"XE \"快速排列图标\"XE \"跨屏移动图标\"XE \"快速拨打电话\"XE \"快速接听电话\"XE \"自动排列图标\"XE \"手掌动作\"XE \"覆盖屏幕\"XE \"魅影触控\"XE \"双击\"XE \"滑动\"XE \"画字母\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>背景信息</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>使用手势控制，可以让您通过简单的动作控制手机，如翻转静音、快速拨打或接听电话。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>操作步骤</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 1  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=188928\" style=\"width:0.24583334in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 2  </span><span>在“全部设置”页签下，点击“手势控制”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 3  </span><span>在“手势控制”界面，点击某一选项，启用对应动作。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>“翻转”：来电、闹钟或计时器响铃或振动时，翻转手机可以静音并停止振动。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=188929\" style=\"width:1.45625in;height:1.2493056in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>“摇一摇”：长按主屏幕空白区域，即可进入主屏幕编辑状态。在主屏幕编辑状态下，摇晃手机可以将散落在屏幕各个位置的图标瞬间排列整齐。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=188930\" style=\"width:1.45625in;height:1.2493056in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span class=\"s3\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1090,"faqType":"开始使用","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5128","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Getting-know-phone","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1447294335000,"seriesProductName":"KIW-AL10,KIW-CL00,KIW-TL00,KIW-TL00H,KIW-UL00","visitedTimes":84,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}